DESCRIPTION:<p>Join us for an exciting <strong>Hackathon</strong> where you
  will obtain hands-on experience in using the <strong>new 
 services</strong> implemented in the <strong>CompBioMed project over the 
 DICE facilities</strong>.</p> <p>Find out how computational biomedical 
 researchers are using the DICE Data Management services to manage their 
 federated data in a FAIR way.</p> <p>If you are a researcher or programmer
